                add 1 to {_slotIndex}
        else if clicked item is iron sword named "&0&0&0&5&r&b아레나 2":
            close player's inventory
            addInventory(1, player, "&0&0&0&5&r&0함꼐 할 파티를 선택해주세요.")
            loop {partylist::%{_player}%::*}:
