                cancel event
            else if "%region at event-block%" contains {@regionArena2}:
                cancel event
        else if event-entity is wither:
            if "%region at event-block%" contains {@regionArena1}:
                cancel event
            else if "%region at event-block%" contains {@regionArena2}:
                cancel event


on place:
